de.dfki.omm.interfaces

Interface OMM

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    OMMImpl, OMMRestImpl

    public interface OMM
    Represents an instance of the OMM (object memory model).
    Please use the methods of OMMFactory to create new OMM instances.
    Author:
    Jens Haupert (jens.haupert@dfki.de)

      • addBlock

        OMMActionResultType addBlock(OMMBlock block,
                             OMMEntity entity)
        Adds a new block to this memory. This block must not contain any OMMEntity as creator/contributor! The creator is set automatically to the given entity.
        Parameters:
        block - the block to add.
        entity - the entity that adds this block
        Returns:
        returns a OMMActionResultType that indicates the result of this action.
